<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="focus-n">focus <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fəʊkəs/    美 /'foʊkəs/  </p>
<p>[C]&amp;<a href="pl focuses/foci">u</a></p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>（光、声等的）焦点；（眼睛、镜头的）焦距：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The focus on my camera isn't working properly.
我的照相机上的调焦装置有毛病。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>（活动、注意力、兴趣等的）中心点/集中点：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The focus of attention has changed.
关注的焦点转移了。</p><footer>外研⑤ – 6</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We shall maintain our <strong>focus on</strong> the needs of the customer.
我们将继续关注顾客的需求。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="bringinto-focuscome-into-focus">bring...into focus/come into focus</h3>
<p>1.<strong>（使）成为焦点</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="in-focus">in focus</h3>
<p>1.<strong>焦点对准的；清晰的</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="out-of-focus">out of focus</h3>
<p>1.<strong>焦点未对准的；模糊不清的</strong>  </p></div>